"""
PART II Entitlement and amount

4A. Meaning of “qualifying young person”

Editorial note: current text valid from 2025-03-21.

(3)

The education or training referred to in paragraph (1) does not include education or training provided by means of a contract of employment.
"""

education_or_training_referred_to_in_paragraph_1_provided_by_means_of_contract_of_employment:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean

qualifying_young_person_4A_3_education_or_training_is_included:
    entity: Person
    period: Day
    dtype: Boolean
    from 2025-03-21:
        if education_or_training_referred_to_in_paragraph_1_provided_by_means_of_contract_of_employment:
            false
        else:
            true
